<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .wrapper {
            background-color: #00205c;
            padding: 0 0;
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 600px;
            border: 2px solid #000000;
        }
        .email-container {
            border-top: 2px solid #000000;
            padding-bottom: 1px;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #00205c;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }
        .header img {
            position: relative;
            width: 150px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-top: -10px;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #385c93;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content p strong {
            color: #F33;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .red-text{
            color:#ff2121;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999999;
        }
        a {
            color: #00205c;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .doubleUnderline {
            text-decoration:underline;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #385c93;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Background Wrapper -->
    <div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <!-- Email Header -->
            <div class="header">
                <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dg2rwod7i/image/upload/v1725984104/xemwtvs7obkdedgyamh1.png" alt="Popular logo">
            </div>
    
            <!-- Email Body -->
            <div class="email-container">
                <div class="content">
                    <p>Hi <span class="red-text">{!Case.Contact}</span>:</p>
                    <p>
                        Please accept our deepest condolences for your loss. We are here to 
                        provide you with the support you need during this difficult time. We 
                        have completed the review of your Liquidation of Funds request under 
                        ticket <span class="red-text">{!Case.CaseNumber}</span>, and we are pleased to confirm that 
                        it has been approved. The amount of <span class="red-text">{!Case.Amount_Disbursed__c}</span> has been deposited 
                        into the account ending in <span class="red-text">{!Case.Disbursement_Account_Number__c}</span>.

                    </p>
                    <p>If you have any questions, you can contact us  at <a href="tel:+17877243650">787-724-3650</a> or visit one of our branches</p>
                    <p>We are here to serve you;<br>
                    Banco Popular de Puerto Rico
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>